      "role": "user",
      "content": "the problem is the doctor just gave me a generic \"don't mix\" answer and didn't really explain why. i'm not like a heavy drinker, just one glass of wine. i just need to sleep so i can work tomorrow. is it really that dangerous if it's just a tiny bit of alcohol? like, won't it just make the zolpidem work more efficiently so i don't have to take more of the pill?",
